  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-19242996-7fff-de4d-9702-9ead8030e9ae&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The applicant has not demonstrated that an acceptable standard of accommodation will be achieved at basement level concerning the provision of light and outlook. The proposal provides substandard accommodation and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; is, therefore, contrary to the guidance in the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009), policies LP1 and LP17 of the Hackney Local Plan (2020), and policy D4 of the London Plan (2021).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.3333px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The proposed front lightwell, by reason of its detailed design and location, is considered to be an inappropriate and unsympathetic addition to the property that is out of keeping with surrounding development. As such the proposal is contrary to policy D4 (Delivering good design)  of the London Plan (2021), policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020), and the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
